---
// WhyBand section — ported verbatim from site/index.html
---
<section id="why" class="why band-dark" aria-label="Why choose Wayne Jones">
  <svg class="band-watermark band-watermark--right" viewBox="0 0 600 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation">
    <use href="#guilloche"></use>
  </svg>

  <div class="section-wrap">
    <header class="section-head section-head--center">
      <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--gold-ink reveal" data-reveal>Why Wayne Jones</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title--light reveal" data-reveal style="--d:1">The difference is <em>personal.</em></h2>
    </header>

    <ol class="manifesto" role="list">
      <li class="manifesto__item reveal" data-reveal>
        <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">I</span>
        <div class="manifesto__body">
          <h3 class="manifesto__title">You work directly with Wayne</h3>
          <p class="manifesto__text">No call centers, no hand-offs. The CPA who reviews your return is the one who answers your call.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="manifesto__item reveal" data-reveal style="--d:1">
        <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">II</span>
        <div class="manifesto__body">
          <h3 class="manifesto__title">Local &amp; accessible</h3>
          <p class="manifesto__text">A familiar face in downtown Rome, not a faceless national chain.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="manifesto__item reveal" data-reveal style="--d:2">
        <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">III</span>
        <div class="manifesto__body">
          <h3 class="manifesto__title">Decades of experience</h3>
          <p class="manifesto__text">35+ years navigating tax law for small businesses and individuals.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="manifesto__item reveal" data-reveal style="--d:3">
        <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">IV</span>
        <div class="manifesto__body">
          <h3 class="manifesto__title">One firm, start to finish</h3>
          <p class="manifesto__text">Books, payroll, and taxes under one roof, with one point of contact.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
